## Product Form (VX) widget

The **Product Form (VX)** widget is made of various components that are displayed based on your [Product type configuration](docs.getvoxel.io_articles_introduction-to-product-types_.md). This is a key widget through which customer makes a purchase, and as such is required to be placed in the Single post template of your Product CPT

Styling options for all the possible components the widget is made of are available on the Style tab of the widget.

No additional settings required.
